      "message": "This is a funny one. I tracked down the CL that added it: https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/c/platform/external/libjpeg-turbo/+/291407/ (I was on the CL, but never chimed in.)\n\nMatt first pushes back on the feature, since the major browsers do not support it. (There is a bug open for Chromium here: https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id\u003d669501. In addition to lack of support, Chromium doesn\u0027t support it because it does not support suspending sources.) But then he has a change of heart and approves it. The original CL description said \"there is no reason not to enable it\", which seems like a bad reason to enable to me...\n\nSo if we were to disable it in Android, that would be a regression from O, though it\u0027s not clear whether anyone would notice.",
